description: Howdy, proud people of Portland! If you’re looking for ample quality in your food, you all just gotta make your way over to Sample This Barbeque.Chef David Sample has been serving up oakwood-smoked Brisket, Sausage, Pulled Pork, and Chicken, along with heavenly homemade sides for over three years, and the locals are always delighted by this succulent Southern-style comfort cuisine. Whether you need your meat piled on a plate, tacos, or nachos, your taste buds will be quite pleased by this Texas-sized treat.
name: Sample This Barbecue
